      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;building-out-a-mini-ios-manga-app&#34;&gt;Building Out a Mini iOS Manga App&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Finally getting back into building iOS apps after a ~2 year hiatus. It&amp;rsquo;s been awhile since I built something outside of work. I started with watching some CS193P lectures&#xA;and followed along for a few lectures before I got bored and decided the best&#xA;way to learn is to build anything ASAP.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Personally I think using AI tools is awful when learning something new and&#xA;having it write the code for you is awful. I use it strictly for learning purposes like &amp;ldquo;Explain Swift Concurrency&amp;rdquo; or &amp;ldquo;Is my code idiomatic?&amp;rdquo; or hints on&#xA;how to approach a problem&lt;/p&gt;</description>
